"Change Set:		8309Kernel-ul.312Kernel-ul.312:Added #scaledIdentityHash.Part 1 of updating Object >> hash."!!Object methodsFor: 'comparing' stamp: 'ul 12/1/2009 04:16'!hash	"Answer a SmallInteger whose value is related to the receiver's identity.	May be overridden, and should be overridden in any classes that define = "	CollectionRehashingUtility quickRehashBecause: #objectHashChanged.	^self scaledIdentityHash! !!ProtoObject methodsFor: 'comparing' stamp: 'ul 11/30/2009 23:54'!scaledIdentityHash	"For identityHash values returned by primitive 75, answer	such values times 2^18.  Otherwise, match the existing	identityHash implementation"	^self identityHash * 262144 "bitShift: 18"! !!SmallInteger methodsFor: 'comparing' stamp: 'ul 11/30/2009 23:55'!scaledIdentityHash	"For identityHash values returned by primitive 75, answer	such values times 2^18.  Otherwise, match the existing	identityHash implementation"		^self! !